[The reference for the research paper cited above is
Welch D, Buonanno M, Grilj V, et al. Far-UVC light: A new tool to control the spread of airborne-mediated microbial diseases. Sci Rep. 2018; 8: 2752; available at https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-018-21058-w

A promising research that can perhaps be piloted, keeping in mind the risk associated with human exposure to UV light. - Mod.UBA]
